categories.name: Tables
categories.description: Our products are entirely handmade and original. They are made upon client’s request and can therefore be customized accordingly. We use several types of wood from our local region, Chouf Lebanon. We apply a variety of epoxy resin depending on multiple variables. These art pieces are designed ergonomically, to be steady and durable.
